 137, \"to\": 150}, {\"ngram\": \"clips\", \"from\": 176, \"to\": 181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The U.S. women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s national basketball team does not often find itself in close games.\\u00c2 Seeking an eighth consecutive gold medal, the squad arrived in Paris carrying an Olympic record of 72\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00933, with the most recent of those losses from before most of this roster was even born.\", \"from\": 206, \"to\": 485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 358, \"end\": 363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999975757419, \"rank\": 2.4243820606928977e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The U.S. women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s national basketball team\", \"from\": 206, \"to\": 249}, {\"ngram\": \"close games\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 291}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 293}, {\"ngram\": \"an eighth consecutive gold medal\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 334}, {\"ngram\": \"the squad\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 345}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic record\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 389}, {\"ngram\": \"72\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00933\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 399}, {\"ngram\": \"those losses\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"this roster\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(It came against the Soviet Unified Team in 1992.)\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 507, \"end\": 513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soviet_Union\", \"score\": 0.9999999766687326, \"rank\": 2.2695954991286508e-08, \"text\": \"Soviet\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soviet_Union\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soviet_Union\"}, {\"begin\": 514, \"end\": 526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unified_Team_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9997466923986371, \"rank\": 0.00025337178252085607, \"text\": \"Unifie