 seriously pressure the U.S.?\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 990, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"There\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"one\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 889}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 933}, {\"ngram\": \"The most recent country\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Belgium.\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 991, \"end\": 998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9980911649605986, \"rank\": 0.0018747648324992433, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And next up in group play for the U.S.?\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1039, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"group play\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1025}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1038}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Belgium.\\u00c2 The country is not exactly known as an international basketball powerhouse.\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1126, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Belgium\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1049}, {\"ngram\": \"The country\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1061}, {\"ngram\": \"an international basketball powerhouse\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But at an Olympic qualifying game in February, the Americans needed a buzzer beater to defeat the Belgians, escaping with a final score of 81\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009379.\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1274, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic qualifying game\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1160}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1172}, {\"ngram\": \"the Americans\", \